$ Encapsulation
   ----> Encapsulation is a way of bundling up or binding the data and the action over the data together and 
   also providing a limited access over it.
   
   ----> There are 4 Access modifiers used
     1. Private     : Only access within the class
     2. Default     : Only access within the package
     3. Protected   : Only access with the inherited class (become public or be protected)
     4. Public      : Access anywhere
     
     From 1->4 Privileges reduces 
    